data.description: NEW PRICE ADJUSTMENT!!!!  This  beautiful home is in the Gateway Community of Cypress Cay.  Home boasts of 5 upstairs bedrooms, do you need to work from home? No problem, it includes a downstairs office/den and 2.5 baths. It offers formal dining and living as well as a family great room off the kitchen. The kitchen has been updated and features new backsplash tile. The master bedroom is huge and has two walk in closets plus a bathroom that has double sinks, jetted tub and separate shower. Bedrooms upstairs are sizable as well with an upstairs laundry room strategically located. This beautiful home sits on a pie shaped, oversized lot on a cul de sac. It has large backyard & lots of green space, room for pool, & can be fenced. Community is pet friendly and has a dog park just up the street within Gateway. The HOA fees are very low. Cypress Cay has it's own community pool and Gateway offers, parks, play areas, soccer fields, Golf and so much more. Close to I-75, International airport, Florida Gulf Coast University, Red Sox & Twins spring training parks, shopping, restaurants, entertainment & more.
